  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT54">
<l>tēvarāy niṟkumat tēvumat tēvaril</l>
<l>mūvarāy niṟku mutupuṇarppum yāvarāy</l>
<l>niṟkiṉṟa tellām neṭumāleṉ ṟōrātār</l>
<l>kaṟkiṉṟa tellām kaṭai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All the learning of people who do not know that</l>
<l>the tall Māl is everyone - [namely,] that Deity who stands among the gods,</l>
<l rend="indent">the ancient creator who stands [among] the trinity among those gods,</l>
<l rend="indent">and He who stands as everyone—</l>
<l>is inferior.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
